  .call-to-action-content
    h3
      | Add a
      strong Task
    p
      | 
      strong Its free
      |  And always will be
  .call-to-action-btn.mt-lg
   a.popup-with-form.btn.btn-primary(href='#/addtask') Add Task!
.heading.heading-border.heading-middle-border.heading-middle-border-center(ng-show='noData')
